📖 Surah Aal-e-Imran 3:104

Arabic:
وَلْتَكُن مِّنكُمْ أُمَّةٌ يَدْعُونَ إِلَى الْخَيْرِ وَيَأْمُرُونَ بِالْمَعْرُوفِ وَيَنْهَوْنَ عَنِ الْمُنكَرِ ۚ وَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْمُفْلِحُونَ

Transliteration:
Wal takun minkum ummatuny yad‘oona ilal khairi wa ya’muroona bil ma‘roofi wa yanhawna ‘anil munkar; wa ulaaa’ika humul muflihoon.

Translation (Roman Urdu):
“Tum mein ek aisi jamaat honi chahiye jo logon ko bhalai ki taraf bulaye, nek kaam ka hukm de, aur burai se roke. Yeh hi log asal mein kamiyab hain.”

🔹 Tafseer / Explanation in Roman Urdu

Allah Ta‘ala keh rahe hain ke har Muslim society mein ek jamaat / group hona chahiye jo actively da‘wah kare.

“Amr bil ma‘roof” = logon ko nek kaam ki taraf motivate karna (namaz, ikhlaq, insaaf, haya).

“Nahy anil munkar” = burai se rokna (zulm, jhoot, gussa, hasad, gunah).

Yeh ayat humein batati hai ke asal success (falah) unhi logon ke liye hai jo apna waqt aur energy Allah ki deen ki khidmat mein lagate hain.

🌟 Relevance for GIO

✅ GIO ka mission bhi isi ayat par hai — ek community of sisters jo Islam ki dawat, bhalai aur akhlaq ko promote karein.
✅ Har member ko yeh ehsaas hona chahiye ke woh is “ummat” ka hissa hai jo Qur’an ne mention ki.

💡 Interactive Question for Session

👉 Aapko kya lagta hai:

“Amr bil ma‘roof” (nek kaam ki taraf bulana) mein sabse important kaam aaj youth ke liye kya hai?

Aur “Nahy anil munkar” (burai se rokna) mein sabse badi zimmedari aapko kahan lagti hai?

